Honeybee Princess Academy ðŸ˜ŠðŸ’–

After a special invitation arrives with your name on it, we get you ready for your first day at the Honeybee Princess Academy; complete with a magic wand, a handmade gown, and a sparkling tiara.

When we arrive at the castle-like Academy, you learn the Principles of Princessingâ€¦which it seems you already know well.

Because of your astute knowledge of what it means to be a Princess, you are immediately given your first quest! Along the way, your senses will be heightened, your princess abilities will be sharpened, and youâ€™ll even meet a new friend: a dragonfly that will become your best-kept secret princess power. Join me, Mr. Honeybee, Melodybee, and Harold for a grand adventure fit for a Princess! But not just any princessâ€¦..this adventure is one for the Honeybee Princess!

Note: I've received sooooo many requests to turn this series into a personalized story...I hope you enjoy ðŸ’–ðŸ’– - Love, Mrs. Honeybee

FAQ:

What is a personalized story?

Mrs. Honeybee will read a bedtime story to youâ€¦using your name!

Go on a special adventure and hear your name all throughout the story ðŸ˜ŠðŸ’–

How long is this story?

This story is 100 minutes long and will include your name at least 10 times.

Can my story have more than 1 name in it?

Most stories yes, but for the Princess Academy only 1 name can be used in this story.

Can I buy from anywhere in the world?

Yes! Use your country's currency and our site will convert it to USD for you.

When will I receive my personalized story?

You will receive your story within 5-6 days of ordering ðŸ˜ŠðŸ’–

How do I listen to my story?

Your story is an .MP3 file (just like a song) and playable from any phone, tablet, or computer.
